OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1777464668
OL,3,CA1M closed for more than 12 hours
OL,4,Cafter serious crash
OL,6,FThe A1M was closed for more than 12
OL,7,Fhours following a serious crash in
OL,8,FCounty Durham.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,11,Fcrash understood to have involved one
OL,12,Fcar on the northbound carriageway
OL,13,Fbetween J62 (Durham) and J63 (Chester
OL,14,Fle Street) at 11:56pm on Sunday 26
OL,15,FApril.
OL,17,FThe North East Ambulance Service
OL,18,F(NEAS) said two males were taken to
OL,19,Fthe Royal Victoria Infirmary in
OL,20,FNewcastle, one in a critical condition.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
