OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1777464668
OL,3,CA1M closed for more than 12 hours
OL,4,Cafter serious crash
OL,6,FBoth carriageways were confirmed to
OL,7,Fhave been reopened shortly after
OL,8,F12:30pm.
OL,10,FA spokesperson for NEAS said the
OL,11,Fservice was called to the serious
OL,12,Fcollision last night by police.
OL,14,F"We sent six resources to the scene
OL,15,Fincluding a duty officer, Hazardous
OL,16,FArea Response Team, a doctor and
OL,17,Femergency ambulance crews, which began
OL,18,Farriving at the scene from 22.59
OL,19,Fonwards," they added.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/3
