OL,3,CA1M closed for more than 12 hours
OL,4,Cafter serious crash
OL,6,F"We took two male patients to the
OL,7,FRoyal Victoria Infirmary in Newcastle,
OL,8,Fone of which was in a critical
OL,9,Fcondition, for further treatment."
